WEBVTT

00:55.840 --> 00:57.440
What does the question mean?

00:57.960 --> 00:58.960
Read it out loud.

00:59.360 --> 01:00.400
On the park lawn,

01:00.400 --> 01:02.000
people wander and linger,

01:02.000 --> 01:03.560
and throw fruit peels and paper scraps.

01:03.560 --> 01:05.489
Please design a slogan for the lawn

01:05.519 --> 01:07.680
to urge pedestrians to protect it.

01:08.440 --> 01:09.920
Look at what you wrote.

01:10.640 --> 01:11.480
Read it out loud.

01:11.480 --> 01:13.880
Today you step on its head,

01:13.880 --> 01:16.360
tomorrow it grows on your grave.

01:16.920 --> 01:19.160
What is all this mess?

01:20.520 --> 01:22.380
Did you copy it from the internet?

01:24.880 --> 01:25.340
Enough.

01:26.160 --> 01:27.680
Rewrite it ten times.

01:33.759 --> 01:36.000
Sister, you're finally back.

01:36.840 --> 01:37.920
Let me tell you,

01:37.920 --> 01:40.650
looking for your sister won't help, understand?

01:40.800 --> 01:42.000
Sister, what is this?

01:42.000 --> 01:43.259
Did you bring it for me?

01:43.960 --> 01:44.560
Xiaocen,

01:44.960 --> 01:46.920
why did you bring a balloon back?

01:48.080 --> 01:49.560
Is it for me?

01:49.560 --> 01:50.920
I don't want it. So childish.

01:50.920 --> 01:52.180
How could it be for you?

01:55.800 --> 01:57.400
Aunt, look at my sister.

01:57.400 --> 01:58.720
She just smiles and ignores your questions,

01:58.720 --> 02:00.040
and wastes her time on toys.

02:00.040 --> 02:01.760
You should go teach her a lesson.

02:01.760 --> 02:03.840
You're full of excuses now, aren't you?

02:03.840 --> 02:04.640
Sit back down.

02:11.560 --> 02:12.280
Xu Xiao,

02:12.920 --> 02:14.440
thank you for the balloon.

02:17.440 --> 02:18.370
You're welcome.

02:18.840 --> 02:19.970
I'm glad you like it.

02:44.000 --> 02:46.120
The ceramic stapling technique can repair porcelain.

02:46.120 --> 02:47.360
For your artwork,

02:48.000 --> 02:49.680
ceramic stapling can help you put the sherds

02:49.680 --> 02:51.120
together more securely.

02:52.079 --> 02:53.610
But kintsugi is different.

02:53.760 --> 02:55.880
Kintsugi can repair not only porcelain

02:55.880 --> 02:58.200
but also wood, ivory, bamboo, jade,

02:58.480 --> 02:59.800
purple clay, and other materials.

02:59.800 --> 03:00.520
In this way,

03:00.600 --> 03:01.680
you can use

03:01.680 --> 03:03.400
more materials in your artwork.

03:03.400 --> 03:04.360
There is more space

03:04.360 --> 03:06.020
to unleash your imagination.

03:09.560 --> 03:10.560
You are bleeding.

03:11.280 --> 03:11.810
I'm fine.

03:13.040 --> 03:14.040
Where is the first-aid kit?

03:14.040 --> 03:14.700
Over there.

03:17.120 --> 03:17.680
Xia Qing.

03:18.800 --> 03:19.400
Let me see.

03:21.079 --> 03:21.560
Look.

03:23.640 --> 03:24.370
Does it hurt?

03:24.760 --> 03:25.420
Be careful.

03:25.640 --> 03:26.170
I'm fine.

03:26.560 --> 03:27.320
It's okay.

03:27.760 --> 03:28.600
I'm used to it

03:29.160 --> 03:30.020
over the years.

03:30.440 --> 03:31.440
I can handle it myself.

03:31.440 --> 03:32.040
Thank you.

04:12.080 --> 04:12.810
You're back.

04:13.080 --> 04:14.160
Mom, Aunt.

04:14.440 --> 04:15.040
Xiaocen.

04:16.079 --> 04:16.880
Are you tired?

04:17.320 --> 04:18.040
I'm fine.

04:19.200 --> 04:20.000
Let me tell you,

04:20.000 --> 04:21.800
you shouldn't go to that studio.

04:23.120 --> 04:24.480
I really shouldn't.

04:27.880 --> 04:28.320
Look,

04:28.480 --> 04:30.940
she went right back in as soon as she got home.

04:53.480 --> 04:55.360
What kept you busy today?

05:00.520 --> 05:01.920
What am I trying to say?

05:06.520 --> 05:08.760
What am I so sad about?

05:19.320 --> 05:19.850
Xiaocen.

05:21.320 --> 05:21.850
Morning.

05:22.880 --> 05:23.410
Morning.

05:24.120 --> 05:25.180
Why did you get here

05:25.920 --> 05:26.780
so early today?

05:31.200 --> 05:32.920
Did everything go well this weekend

05:32.920 --> 05:34.800
with Xia Qing?

05:35.159 --> 05:36.290
It went pretty well.

05:37.040 --> 05:38.900
Xia Qing has made great progress.

05:39.000 --> 05:41.360
Whether it's ceramic stapling or kintsugi,

05:41.360 --> 05:43.620
she has mastered some basic techniques.

05:45.720 --> 05:47.050
We are preparing to make

05:47.120 --> 05:48.880
a piece with more complex craftsmanship.

05:48.880 --> 05:52.340
We plan to combine broken porcelain pieces, bamboo, and wood.

05:52.760 --> 05:54.890
You'll see when you come to the studio.

05:56.120 --> 05:56.720
By the way.

05:58.320 --> 06:00.920
Why didn't you come to the studio this weekend?

06:04.520 --> 06:05.600
I was wondering

06:06.640 --> 06:08.920
if Xia Qing doesn't need me anymore.

06:10.200 --> 06:11.600
Why would you think that?

06:13.760 --> 06:15.480
Didn't you see it too?

06:17.040 --> 06:18.920
I can't be of any help if I go.

06:19.920 --> 06:21.720
Xia Qing was afraid I'd feel awkward,

06:21.720 --> 06:23.650
so she found something for me to do.

06:25.280 --> 06:26.280
What's the point?

06:27.520 --> 06:28.980
Don't you think you should

06:29.640 --> 06:31.240
discuss this with everyone?

06:34.120 --> 06:36.080
You can just tell Xia Qing.

06:36.200 --> 06:38.130
Since you guys are so close anyway.

06:38.600 --> 06:39.730
That's so impolite.

06:43.960 --> 06:44.520
Xiaocen.

06:46.159 --> 06:49.080
I remember you're not the kind of person to give up halfway.

06:49.080 --> 06:49.920
What's wrong with you?

06:49.920 --> 06:51.580
I just don't want to go anyway.

06:58.960 --> 07:01.400
Every day, only Xu Xiao arrives earlier than me.

07:01.400 --> 07:02.200
It seems our class

07:02.200 --> 07:04.080
is getting another good student.

07:05.960 --> 07:07.490
I just finished streaming.

07:08.520 --> 07:10.050
Come have some watermelon.

07:12.840 --> 07:15.240
Xu Xiao is back. Come have some watermelon.

07:15.480 --> 07:16.880
You guys go ahead and eat.

07:17.360 --> 07:18.080
Where is Xiaocen?

07:18.080 --> 07:20.480
Didn't she say she'd come over after class?

07:21.560 --> 07:22.560
She's not coming.

07:22.760 --> 07:24.160
Something came up again?

07:25.320 --> 07:26.780
She's never coming again.

07:27.240 --> 07:28.440
I'll go inside first.

07:32.560 --> 07:33.820
What's wrong with him?

07:34.480 --> 07:35.409
What's going on?

08:27.320 --> 08:27.800
Class,

08:28.280 --> 08:31.280
At this stage, we have learned kintsugi restoration.

08:31.600 --> 08:33.159
Regarding kintsugi restoration,

08:33.159 --> 08:34.159
since ancient times,

08:34.159 --> 08:35.840
there has been controversy.

08:36.240 --> 08:38.400
Should kintsugi restoration

08:38.400 --> 08:40.860
maintain the original beauty of the object,

08:41.559 --> 08:43.120
or should it undergo a

08:43.360 --> 08:45.160
What about secondary creation?

08:46.480 --> 08:48.240
Respecting the original beauty of the object

08:48.240 --> 08:49.600
and giving it a new appearance

08:49.600 --> 08:51.120
are actually not contradictory.

08:51.120 --> 08:52.920
I think a good restorer

08:53.200 --> 08:55.460
can find a certain balance between them.

08:56.960 --> 08:57.560
Very good.

08:58.480 --> 09:00.340
When we restore cultural relics,

09:00.400 --> 09:01.160
sometimes

09:01.240 --> 09:03.800
we have to converse with history.

09:04.880 --> 09:06.000
But sometimes,

09:07.000 --> 09:10.520
we may have to connect with the future.

09:10.760 --> 09:11.480
If

09:11.800 --> 09:13.040
we treat an object

09:13.160 --> 09:14.640
as a person,

09:14.880 --> 09:16.480
a person needs to persevere.

09:16.560 --> 09:19.120
But don't we also need to learn,

09:19.480 --> 09:21.680
constantly develop, and change

09:21.840 --> 09:23.120
to improve ourselves?

09:24.280 --> 09:25.740
Regarding this question,

09:25.760 --> 09:28.680
I hope everyone can come up with their own answers.

09:38.200 --> 09:40.200
Are you going back to the classroom?

09:43.400 --> 09:44.530
Where are you going?

09:45.360 --> 09:47.690
I'm handing in my assignment to Mr. Liang.

09:52.520 --> 09:55.520
How is your project with Sister Xia Qing coming along?

09:57.200 --> 10:00.080
The artwork for the exhibition is basically done.

10:03.480 --> 10:04.520
See, I told you.

10:06.200 --> 10:08.800
It won't make a difference if I'm not there.

10:12.400 --> 10:12.680
Actually,

10:12.680 --> 10:13.800
how did you do on the exam, Zhu Pan?

10:13.800 --> 10:14.640
I did okay.

10:14.640 --> 10:15.400
I did pretty well.

10:15.400 --> 10:16.800
These are all from the scope the professor gave us.

10:16.800 --> 10:17.800
When was it given?

10:17.800 --> 10:18.480
Why don't I remember?

10:18.480 --> 10:19.480
Wasn't it sent to the group chat?

10:19.480 --> 10:20.840
You just didn't check the messages.

10:20.840 --> 10:22.520
If you saw it, why didn't you tell me?

10:22.520 --> 10:24.250
That's your own problem, okay?

10:24.560 --> 10:26.620
Actually, I didn't help much either.

10:27.200 --> 10:28.200
Xiaqing

10:28.840 --> 10:30.900
has always been an excellent person.

10:32.160 --> 10:32.840
Unlike me,

10:33.040 --> 10:34.640
I'm slow at learning everything.

10:34.640 --> 10:35.280
No.

10:36.960 --> 10:37.520
Xiaocen.

10:39.040 --> 10:39.920
To me,

10:40.280 --> 10:42.810
you've always been a very important partner.

10:47.240 --> 10:49.000
Right. It's always like this.

10:49.360 --> 10:50.560
Excuse me.

10:52.760 --> 10:54.890
Why do they always make us move things?

10:55.200 --> 10:56.860
Can't they find someone else?

10:57.360 --> 10:58.000
Exactly.

10:58.040 --> 10:59.000
Excuse me.

10:59.440 --> 11:00.240
Slow down.

11:00.240 --> 11:01.520
They asked you last time,

11:01.520 --> 11:02.480
and now they asked me.

11:02.480 --> 11:03.680
Yes, exactly.

11:13.960 --> 11:15.320
Then I'll get going.

11:18.600 --> 11:19.320
Xu Xiao.

11:22.320 --> 11:23.580
About the exhibition,

11:25.480 --> 11:27.880
I thought of some people who could help you.

11:59.320 --> 12:00.520
Careful coming down.

12:00.680 --> 12:01.280
Watch out.

12:01.520 --> 12:02.240
Xiaqing.

12:02.520 --> 12:03.320
Put it here?

12:03.600 --> 12:04.660
Put it on the shelf.

12:04.680 --> 12:05.280
Slow down.

12:05.480 --> 12:05.880
Okay.

12:16.960 --> 12:18.280
There are cold and hot ones.

12:18.280 --> 12:18.960
Careful.

12:19.040 --> 12:19.560
Hold it.

12:19.560 --> 12:21.220
Pass it over. Pass it that way.

12:21.240 --> 12:22.080
I'll have the matcha one.

12:22.080 --> 12:23.040
Here, this is for you.

12:23.040 --> 12:23.500
Thanks.

12:23.800 --> 12:24.280
Are there any others?

12:24.280 --> 12:25.410
Have a cup, Xiaqing.

12:25.880 --> 12:26.400
Any more straws?

12:26.400 --> 12:26.800
Straws.

12:26.800 --> 12:27.200
You drink it.

12:27.200 --> 12:27.720
Give me another cup.

12:27.720 --> 12:28.040
Here are some more.

12:28.040 --> 12:28.320
Thanks.

12:28.320 --> 12:29.480
Who doesn't have a straw yet?

12:29.480 --> 12:31.940
Since everyone is here, I'll say a few words.

12:32.360 --> 12:34.480
Thank you all very much for coming today

12:34.480 --> 12:35.120
and helping us out.

12:35.120 --> 12:36.200
On behalf of the studio,

12:36.200 --> 12:37.800
I sincerely thank everyone.

12:38.400 --> 12:39.560
You're too polite, Jingjing.

12:39.560 --> 12:40.280
It's the least we could do.

12:40.280 --> 12:42.000
I believe this exhibition will be a huge success.

12:42.000 --> 12:43.120
We'll all come and see it.

12:43.120 --> 12:44.450
Let me tell you a secret.

12:45.040 --> 12:46.900
I've invested my entire net worth

12:47.720 --> 12:48.980
into this exhibition.

12:49.040 --> 12:50.240
So please, everyone,

12:50.680 --> 12:52.200
on WeChat and Weibo,

12:52.680 --> 12:54.200
help me promote it.

12:55.080 --> 12:56.560
If you help me promote it,

12:57.440 --> 12:59.370
I'll cover your milk tea for a week.

12:59.600 --> 13:00.320
That's great.

13:00.320 --> 13:01.240
Thank you, Jing.

13:01.240 --> 13:02.240
Jing is so generous.

13:02.240 --> 13:03.000
Jing is so generous.

13:03.000 --> 13:04.660
We should start promoting it.

13:15.800 --> 13:16.120
Then...

13:16.120 --> 13:16.680
Well...

13:22.280 --> 13:23.410
Get some rest early.

13:26.520 --> 13:27.180
Good night.

13:28.360 --> 13:29.020
Good night.

13:47.200 --> 13:48.720
I should apologize to him

13:49.200 --> 13:50.680
for the studio issue.

14:44.480 --> 14:46.000
Of course he likes you.

14:46.280 --> 14:47.720
He doesn't get off at that stop,

14:47.720 --> 14:49.760
but he insists on walking you home every time.

14:49.760 --> 14:52.020
If that's not liking you, then what is it?

14:52.920 --> 14:54.000
It's possible

14:54.200 --> 14:55.560
that he's just a really nice guy

14:55.560 --> 14:57.600
and is worried about my safety going back alone.

14:57.600 --> 14:58.320
Come on.

14:58.600 --> 14:59.440
If he's really that nice,

14:59.440 --> 15:01.700
why doesn't he walk the whole class home?

15:06.680 --> 15:08.340
Then Yuexin, what should I do?

15:15.040 --> 15:15.680
Xiaocen.

15:16.120 --> 15:17.320
Have you ever thought

15:17.840 --> 15:18.760
that you

15:19.200 --> 15:21.880
don't necessarily have to wait for him to make the first move?

15:21.880 --> 15:22.920
I think we girls

15:22.920 --> 15:26.120
can also take the initiative to pursue the people we like.

15:28.360 --> 15:29.160
What's wrong?

15:29.600 --> 15:31.640
I still can't believe he likes me.

15:32.400 --> 15:33.320
Why?

15:33.680 --> 15:35.280
You're so pretty, smart,

15:35.480 --> 15:36.480
and hardworking.

15:36.600 --> 15:38.660
If I were Xu Xiao, I would like you too.

15:39.680 --> 15:40.920
Thank you, Yuexin.

15:40.920 --> 15:41.800
Be confident.

16:03.280 --> 16:03.880
Yuexin.

16:04.400 --> 16:05.600
You're finally here.

16:07.960 --> 16:08.800
This is really well made.

16:08.800 --> 16:10.660
This one. This one looks the best.

16:38.680 --> 16:39.400
We'll get going then.

16:39.400 --> 16:40.000
Bye.

16:40.000 --> 16:41.040
Bye.

16:41.040 --> 16:41.760
Thanks. Bye.

16:41.760 --> 16:42.360
Take care.

16:45.240 --> 16:46.640
It's already afternoon.

16:46.720 --> 16:48.580
Why are only regulars showing up?

16:52.120 --> 16:53.720
Walk-ins aren't important.

16:53.720 --> 16:55.320
The important one is Mr. Qin.

16:55.320 --> 16:57.450
As long as Mr. Qin likes Xiaqing's work

16:57.720 --> 16:59.640
and invests in our brand,

17:00.000 --> 17:01.930
this exhibition will be a success.

17:05.839 --> 17:06.839
This glaze color is really beautiful.

17:06.839 --> 17:07.160
Yes.

17:07.240 --> 17:09.170
Please don't mind the small scale.

17:11.160 --> 17:11.760
Tianyuan.

17:13.200 --> 17:13.599
Come.

17:17.240 --> 17:18.440
Let me introduce you.

17:18.599 --> 17:19.880
These are the partners

17:19.880 --> 17:21.079
of our Banlan Studio.

17:21.720 --> 17:22.480
Let me specially introduce

17:22.480 --> 17:23.480
this one.

17:23.599 --> 17:25.079
This is our ceramic artist,

17:25.079 --> 17:25.880
Fang Xiaqing.

17:26.680 --> 17:26.960
Nice to meet you.

17:26.960 --> 17:27.819
Hello, Mr. Qin.

17:28.840 --> 17:31.120
Next, we'll let Xiaqing

17:31.120 --> 17:32.080
show you around.

17:32.080 --> 17:33.280
She can introduce things to you.

17:33.280 --> 17:33.720
Okay.

17:34.360 --> 17:35.620
Come, please this way.

17:37.400 --> 17:38.040
This is

17:38.040 --> 17:40.040
our main exhibition area this time.

17:40.520 --> 17:41.520
We also have

17:41.520 --> 17:43.320
many excellent works this time.

17:43.360 --> 17:44.960
The name of this work is "Glory",

17:44.960 --> 17:47.220
because it shines like butterfly wings.

17:47.320 --> 17:48.050
And this work

17:48.160 --> 17:49.480
is called "Bad Company".

17:49.480 --> 17:51.800
One of the porcelain pieces has the word Ziqi engraved on it.

17:51.800 --> 17:52.960
Perhaps this name...

17:52.960 --> 17:54.890
Mr. Qin keeps nodding and smiling.

17:55.200 --> 17:56.460
This looks promising.

17:56.920 --> 17:57.840
Really?

17:58.520 --> 18:00.780
He seems to be just responding politely.

18:04.920 --> 18:06.580
I've looked at all your works.

18:06.840 --> 18:07.970
They're quite good.

18:08.680 --> 18:10.560
I'll keep following your work.

18:11.880 --> 18:12.760
Please, don't see me out.

18:12.760 --> 18:13.290
Goodbye.

18:13.600 --> 18:14.600
I'll walk you out.

18:14.680 --> 18:15.280
Take care.

18:37.840 --> 18:38.970
What did Mr. Qin say?

18:42.600 --> 18:43.330
Pretty good.

18:43.960 --> 18:44.720
He said

18:45.280 --> 18:47.480
he really appreciates Xiaqing's works.

18:47.480 --> 18:49.520
He also thinks Xiaqing has the potential

18:49.520 --> 18:50.650
to become an artist.

18:54.360 --> 18:55.600
But

18:56.600 --> 18:59.360
he thinks Xiaqing's works are too intricate

18:59.800 --> 19:00.680
and too unique.

19:01.560 --> 19:03.280
So, as commercial products,

19:03.880 --> 19:05.610
they are hard to mass-produce.

19:24.200 --> 19:25.330
Let's drink a toast.

19:25.720 --> 19:26.280
Cheers.

19:44.840 --> 19:46.640
I have something to tell you all.

19:49.160 --> 19:50.160
We might

19:51.840 --> 19:53.370
have to move out next month.

19:54.960 --> 19:55.760
Move out?

19:56.800 --> 19:58.160
The studio's equipment,

19:58.160 --> 19:59.200
rent, utilities,

19:59.520 --> 20:00.520
daily expenses,

20:00.880 --> 20:02.480
including this exhibition.

20:03.600 --> 20:05.000
I've emptied my savings.

20:06.000 --> 20:08.320
I thought Mr. Qin could invest

20:10.080 --> 20:12.160
so we could pay next month's rent.

20:15.560 --> 20:17.360
Can't we live together anymore?

20:17.360 --> 20:19.690
I was thinking we rent a small place first,

20:19.920 --> 20:21.920
and then when we get through this period

20:21.920 --> 20:23.600
and have some money on hand...

20:27.680 --> 20:28.440
Actually,

20:29.080 --> 20:30.140
I'm also wondering

20:30.160 --> 20:32.020
if I should move out of Jingdezhen

20:32.800 --> 20:34.330
and go back to a regular job.

20:34.360 --> 20:35.690
Why are you leaving too?

20:36.360 --> 20:37.890
I'm just thinking about it.

20:40.960 --> 20:41.760
It's my fault.

20:43.520 --> 20:44.120
I'm sorry.

20:44.240 --> 20:45.700
I disappointed everyone.

20:45.800 --> 20:46.800
Don't think like that.

20:46.800 --> 20:47.960
Yeah, Xiaqing.

20:48.000 --> 20:49.200
It's not your fault.

20:51.040 --> 20:52.240
If anyone is to blame, it's that Mr. Qin.

20:52.240 --> 20:53.120
Stop it.

20:56.480 --> 20:57.560
It's my problem.

20:58.200 --> 20:59.400
I was too naive.

21:03.360 --> 21:04.690
I wanted to win too much.

21:04.760 --> 21:07.360
I didn't understand the business model at all.

21:08.560 --> 21:09.760
I lost, and I admit it.

21:12.200 --> 21:14.060
What just makes me feel a bit bad is

21:16.160 --> 21:17.880
that I made you work for nothing for so long.

21:17.880 --> 21:19.010
I feel really sorry.

21:19.120 --> 21:20.120
Don't say that.

21:20.760 --> 21:21.560
Not at all.

21:32.520 --> 21:33.440
We didn't lose.

21:36.800 --> 21:37.880
At least Xia Qing's works

21:37.880 --> 21:38.960
truly moved me.

21:40.280 --> 21:41.400
Especially the one

21:42.200 --> 21:43.330
called 'freshman'.

21:45.160 --> 21:46.360
Although I don't know

21:47.000 --> 21:49.330
why that piece has no story introduction,

21:50.160 --> 21:51.880
I saw a kind of power in it.

21:53.160 --> 21:54.440
A power that I need

21:55.200 --> 21:56.560
but lack.

22:00.320 --> 22:01.120
Sorry, I...

22:01.880 --> 22:03.280
I'm not good at speaking.

22:04.240 --> 22:05.900
What I want to tell everyone is

22:06.960 --> 22:07.880
that we really did

22:07.880 --> 22:09.480
something very meaningful.

22:16.960 --> 22:17.960
Xiaocen is right.

22:22.320 --> 22:23.160
This piece

22:23.560 --> 22:25.760
is something I want to give to all of you.

22:28.320 --> 22:28.960
If

22:29.400 --> 22:31.000
I hadn't come to Jingdezhen,

22:31.400 --> 22:32.460
hadn't met you all,

22:32.960 --> 22:34.760
and if you hadn't recognized me,

22:36.040 --> 22:36.770
accepted me,

22:37.560 --> 22:38.360
supported me,

22:40.200 --> 22:41.200
and protected me,

22:43.120 --> 22:45.720
I wouldn't have had the courage to face my past.

22:46.320 --> 22:47.040
Moreover,

22:48.840 --> 22:51.040
I could never have finished this piece.

22:51.200 --> 22:52.000
So,

22:52.360 --> 22:54.520
this new life is a gift from all of you.

23:10.440 --> 23:11.370
With your words,

23:12.080 --> 23:13.880
I have the courage to start over.

23:14.640 --> 23:15.800
If it doesn't work this time,

23:15.800 --> 23:16.880
we'll try again next time.

23:16.880 --> 23:18.640
It will work out eventually, right?

23:18.640 --> 23:19.680
Yes, absolutely.

23:20.600 --> 23:21.460
Tomorrow we'll

23:21.920 --> 23:23.520
set up a stall in Taoxichuan.

23:23.640 --> 23:25.280
The worst case is just starting over.

23:25.280 --> 23:26.760
What's there to be afraid of?

23:26.760 --> 23:27.160
Right.

23:28.200 --> 23:29.600
Then I won't leave either.

23:29.600 --> 23:30.660
I'll stay with you.

23:31.200 --> 23:32.200
Great, together.

23:33.200 --> 23:34.000
Cheers.

23:34.360 --> 23:35.840
We won't go home until we're drunk tonight.

23:35.840 --> 23:36.440
Cheers.

23:53.960 --> 23:54.490
Xiaocen.

23:56.080 --> 23:57.000
Xia Qing.

24:18.960 --> 24:20.120
Thank you, Xia Qing.

24:21.800 --> 24:22.330
Xiaocen,

24:23.200 --> 24:25.060
what are you doing here all alone?

24:26.320 --> 24:27.680
I'm just spacing out.

24:31.560 --> 24:32.160
Xiaocen.

24:33.480 --> 24:33.920
Here.

24:42.000 --> 24:42.800
You know what?

24:43.600 --> 24:44.440
Actually,

24:45.880 --> 24:48.410
I've always felt that you and I are very alike.

24:55.400 --> 24:57.320
You are so excellent,

24:59.160 --> 24:59.800
while I...

25:00.800 --> 25:01.280
See,

25:02.200 --> 25:04.130
this is the problem with both of us.

25:06.360 --> 25:08.490
We always think we're not good enough.

25:11.320 --> 25:13.440
So even someone as excellent as you

25:14.520 --> 25:16.520
can feel like she's not good enough.

25:18.880 --> 25:19.560
Xiaocen,

25:20.960 --> 25:21.760
you know what?

25:22.320 --> 25:23.800
The creation of 'Freshman'

25:23.800 --> 25:26.460
wouldn't have happened without Xu Xiao's help,

25:26.520 --> 25:29.850
but more importantly, without the inspiration you gave me.

25:29.880 --> 25:30.720
Me?

25:31.160 --> 25:32.360
Haven't you noticed?

25:33.400 --> 25:34.400
Beneath those flowers,

25:34.400 --> 25:35.960
the human face made of ruins

25:36.720 --> 25:39.050
came from the doodles in your sketchbook.

25:44.680 --> 25:45.320
Xiaocen.

25:46.760 --> 25:48.290
If you really like someone,

25:48.960 --> 25:50.090
you have to be brave.

25:50.160 --> 25:51.090
Don't be afraid,

25:51.760 --> 25:52.890
and don't back down.

25:54.000 --> 25:54.930
You must believe

25:55.480 --> 25:57.010
that you are worthy of love.

25:58.360 --> 25:59.620
Worthy of everything.

26:09.800 --> 26:10.840
But...

26:14.400 --> 26:15.480
he and you...

26:17.880 --> 26:18.400
What?

26:19.960 --> 26:21.480
He and you aren't...

26:32.480 --> 26:34.140
Xiaocen, you misunderstood.

26:34.200 --> 26:36.440
That day, Xu Xiao was just bandaging me up.

26:36.440 --> 26:38.240
You're the only one who can't see it.

26:38.240 --> 26:40.320
Everyone in our studio can tell

26:40.320 --> 26:42.050
that he really cares about you.

26:59.840 --> 27:01.770
Thank you for coming to help today,

27:01.840 --> 27:03.370
and giving me so many ideas.

27:03.440 --> 27:05.120
It's fine. Hurry back to school

27:05.120 --> 27:06.040
before it gets late.

27:06.040 --> 27:06.400
Okay.

27:06.480 --> 27:07.120
We'll be leaving then.

27:07.120 --> 27:08.240
Goodbye, Sister Xiaqing.

27:08.240 --> 27:09.120
Bye. Take care.

27:09.560 --> 27:10.080
Alright. Bye.

27:10.080 --> 27:11.000
Watch out for cars.

27:11.000 --> 27:11.600
Take care.

27:35.480 --> 27:36.840
You're the only one who can't tell.

27:36.840 --> 27:38.960
Everyone in our studio can see it.

27:38.960 --> 27:40.420
He really cares about you.

27:59.320 --> 28:00.180
Can I listen...

28:03.440 --> 28:04.240
What's wrong?

28:04.240 --> 28:06.700
Can I listen to the song you're listening to?

28:40.360 --> 28:42.120
Right now, he is by my side.

28:43.520 --> 28:45.380
We are listening to the same song.

28:46.920 --> 28:49.360
I guess this is a step forward.

28:52.680 --> 28:54.610
It's good enough like this for now.

28:55.720 --> 28:57.520
Taking it slow is fine.

28:59.640 --> 29:02.560
There is still a long time left in college.

29:03.800 --> 29:06.600
There will definitely be a right time in the future

29:07.360 --> 29:09.480
when I can express to Xu Xiao

29:09.480 --> 29:11.200
my true feelings.

29:14.840 --> 29:16.370
This is good enough for now.

29:17.800 --> 29:19.000
This is good enough.

29:25.240 --> 29:26.080
I like you.
